?u?l?l?l?l?l?l?d?d
?u?l?l?l?l?l?d?d?d
?u?l?l?l?l?l?l?d?d?d
?u?l?l?l?l?l?d?d?d?d
?u?l?l?l?l?l?l?d?d?d?d

